Package administration.daos

Class AbstractChallengeEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • administration.daos.AbstractChallengeEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Challenge

    @Entity
public abstract class AbstractChallengeEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Max. This class is the abstract entry for a challenge in the database. It includes the id, the version, the creation date and the update date of a challenge.
